{"id":98,"count":1,"description":"Golden Triangle \u2013 India\u2019s most iconic travel circuit, the Golden Triangle connects Delhi, Agra, and Jaipur, offering a perfect introduction to the country\u2019s rich history, culture, and heritage. Begin in Delhi, where ancient monuments like the Red Fort, Qutub Minar, and India Gate stand alongside bustling markets and modern landmarks. Continue to Agra, home to the timeless symbol of love, the Taj Mahal, along with Agra Fort and Fatehpur Sikri. Conclude in the royal city of Jaipur, the Pink City, famous for its majestic forts, palaces, vibrant bazaars, and colorful traditions. This journey forms a triangle on the map, hence the name, and provides travelers with a captivating glimpse into India\u2019s royal past, Mughal grandeur, and vibrant present.","link":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/destinations\/golden-triangle\/","name":"GOLDEN TRIANGLE","slug":"golden-triangle","taxonomy":"destination","parent":0,"meta":[],"thumbnail":{"width":900,"height":596,"file":"2025\/09\/GOLDEN-TRIANGLE.png","filesize":1068144,"sizes":{"medium":{"file":"GOLDEN-TRIANGLE-300x199.png","width":300,"height":199,"filesize":39253,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/GOLDEN-TRIANGLE-300x199.png"},"thumbnail":{"file":"GOLDEN-TRIANGLE-150x150.png","width":150,"height":150,"filesize":18212,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/GOLDEN-TRIANGLE-150x150.png"},"medium_large":{"file":"GOLDEN-TRIANGLE-768x509.png","width":768,"height":509,"filesize":419461,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/GOLDEN-TRIANGLE-768x509.png"},"trip-thumb-size":{"file":"GOLDEN-TRIANGLE-374x226.png","width":374,"height":226,"filesize":51716,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/GOLDEN-TRIANGLE